## Project Overview

Memory is an Android application designed to provide personalized cognitive training rather than a traditional memory game.

Unlike classic memory games that rely on fixed difficulty levels, Memory continuously analyses player behaviour, identifies cognitive patterns and dynamically adjusts future gameplay based on the user's performance.

The project was independently designed, implemented and documented in less than one month using an AI-assisted development workflow.

