## Game Modes

### Adaptive Mode

Automatically adjusts the difficulty level according to the player's current performance.

### Timed Mode

Thirty-two predefined challenges completed under time pressure.

### Challenge Mode

Allows users to compare their results across different board configurations.

---

## Reports

The application stores detailed statistics for every completed session, including:

- score,
- completion time,
- effectiveness,
- board size,
- game mode,
- mistake categories,
- player progress.

Users can generate PDF reports summarizing their training history and cognitive performance.

